Instructions to everyone:-
    Enjoy this archive, keep a lookout for newer versions (probably on the aminet), if you use my code for inspiration then mention me in your docs, don't alter this archive and redistribute it in anyway. If you wish to include one part of the archive (which is one of the directories) then be sure to include the entire subdirectory, along with a little note telling of where you can get the full archive from. e.g. If you wish to include only Eko then be sure to include 
    * Eko
    * Eko.e
    * Eko.guide[.info]
    * READMEFIRST.txt
    Thank's for reading this note, try and wade through the docs and live long and prosper.

        Steven Goodgrove

